{
  "texts": [
    "Leveraging such technologies -say to figure out which situation triggers a certain behavior in someone with ASD, may become part of the evolving role of SLPs.",
    "By automating routine screenings with high accuracy, AI can free SLPs to focus on more complex cases, enhancing the efficiency and reach of speechlanguage services.",
    "SLPs will need additional training in the use of such technologies, and they will need to be careful of data privacy protections.",
    "Assessment in SLP involves diagnosing communication and swallowing disorders using standardized tools and clinical judgment.",
    "AI can enhance this process by drafting case histories from recorded interviews and interactions, thereby allowing SLPs to focus more directly on patient engagement."
  ]
}